Version 3.0

ChangeLog:
* Add OAuth support for twitter and rewrite the code resolving t.co, faster and more stable.

see http://ycflame.com/archives/608.html to learn how to deploy this application.

This application will sync all your tweets except RT and @ to fanfou and digu, and then to the big four SNS platforms 

in China —— Sina microblog, Tencent microblog, Douban and Renren.


